00:29:07.372 --> 00:29:09.208
You want to know something crazy?

475
00:29:09.291 --> 00:29:11.543
I'm the one that reached out
to him this time.

476
00:29:14.630 --> 00:29:16.048
I don't know why I did that.

477
00:29:16.882 --> 00:29:18.050
