490
00:30:13.856 --> 00:30:16.191
<i>Some crashes you can see coming.</i>

491
00:30:16.817 --> 00:30:20.112
<i>There's time to brace for impact
or veer off course.</i>

492
00:30:20.988 --> 00:30:24.783
<i>But some crashes send you hurtling
through space at such velocity</i>

493
00:30:24.867 --> 00:30:27.160
