and then he does community service.

497
00:31:31.433 --> 00:31:34.394
- So. which is... It's good news.
- [Eleanor] I think it's great. right?

498
00:31:35.312 --> 00:31:38.774
[speaking indistinctly]

499
00:31:38.857 --> 00:31:41.026
Because he's gonna get
the help that he needs.

500
00:31:41.109 --> 00:31:43.028
He's not gonna have
a permanent ding on his record.

501
00:31:43.111 --> 00:31:44.780
- And that's so important.
- I have to leave.

502
00:31:44.863 --> 00:31:47.658
- I don't feel good. I'm gonna go home.
- What's wrong? What's... Nancy?

503
00:31:47.741 --> 00:31:49.284
- I... I'm just not well.
- [Eleanor] Nan?

504
00:31:49.368 --> 00:31:51.828
- Are you... Yeah. yeah.
- Should I? Yeah. I'll be right back.

505
00:31:51.912 --> 00:31:53.413
Hey. Nancy.

506
00:31:54.706 --> 00:31:57.042
- Nance! What is going on?
- S-Sorry. I wanna...

507
00:31:57.125 --> 00:31:59.044
I wanna be there for Mare. I just. um...

508
00:32:00.045 --> 00:32:02.256
I just have too much going on right now.

509
00:32:02.339 --> 00:32:03.590
