- Okay.

519
00:32:28.782 --> 00:32:31.034
His name is David.
I... It's not gonna happen again.

520
00:32:31.118 --> 00:32:33.245
- Okay.
- [pants] I have to go.

521
00:32:33.328 --> 00:32:34.705
