wouldn't listen.

564
00:37:32.044 --> 00:37:34.796
No price was too great
to pay to bring her back to life.

565
00:37:35.506 --> 00:37:39.843
This summer. we bid fair winds
and following seas to <i>Demeter's Wish</i>.

566
00:37:39.927 --> 00:37:42.221
