the trust to pay off our investors.

587
00:38:42.406 --> 00:38:44.241
- Is that true?
- [Robert sniffles]

588
00:38:44.324 --> 00:38:46.660
Sometimes you just gotta rip off
the Band-Aid. Bobby.

589
00:38:46.743 --> 00:38:50.038
His name that he uses
in his adult life is Robert.

590
00:38:51.665 --> 00:38:53.041
[Robert] Right. let's go.

591
00:39:28.285 --> 00:39:29.286
[sobs]

592
00:39:32.831 --> 00:39:33.832
[sobs]

593
00:39:35.417 --> 00:39:37.002
Oh. sweetheart.

594
00:39:37.085 --> 00:39:39.004
