595
00:39:42.132 --> 00:39:44.176
I... [stammers] ...I fucked up. Nance.

596
00:39:45.260 --> 00:39:46.261
[clicks tongue]

597
00:39:47.262 --> 00:39:49.181
I really fucked up.

598
00:39:51.558 --> 00:39:52.768
I'm a fuck up.

599
