603
00:40:05.822 --> 00:40:09.201
The house. the cars. your parties.

604
00:40:11.370 --> 00:40:12.955
Everything goes through him.

605
00:40:14.164 --> 00:40:15.499
[inhales sharply]

606
00:40:15.582 --> 00:40:17.835
