so my father couldn't get to it.

618
00:40:55.038 --> 00:40:56.164
Oh. my God.

619
00:40:57.624 --> 00:40:59.960
- You-You-You deserve protection.
- [sniffles]

620
00:41:02.462 --> 00:41:05.883
[chuckles] I don't want a divorce.
I want you.

621
