- Yes. I can.

624
00:41:16.935 --> 00:41:18.228
I can.

625
00:41:19.813 --> 00:41:22.357
I've been living without your love
for three months now

626
00:41:22.441 --> 00:41:26.945
and I'm... [sniffles] ...a total mess.

627
00:41:27.029 --> 00:41:29.990
I don't care about it.
Your dad can take it.

628
00:41:30.073 --> 00:41:31.491
I just want you.

629
