656
00:44:42.140 --> 00:44:43.475
No one ever would.

657
00:44:55.654 --> 00:44:58.782
I'm so happy that
you didn't hate it. [chuckles]

658
00:44:58.866 --> 00:45:00.868
- That I what?
- That you didn't hate it.

659
00:45:00.951 --> 00:45:03.203
Oh. I loved it.
I loved everything about it.

660
00:45:03.287 --> 00:45:06.999
Um. the dancing and the clothes.

661
00:45:07.082 --> 00:45:08.208
Costumes.

662
00:45:08.292 --> 00:45:09.960
The costumes. yeah. That was beautiful.

663
00:45:10.544 --> 00:45:14.298
[Nancy] <i>This was my chance to
course correct and avoid catastrophe.</i>

664
00:45:14.381 --> 00:45:17.551
<i>I had to tell Robert the truth. All of it.</i>

665
00:45:17.634 --> 00:45:19.720
<i>And believe that he would still love me.</i>

666
00:45:19.803 --> 00:45:21.763
