682
00:46:15.817 --> 00:46:17.653
I can't believe this.
I can't believe this.

683
00:46:17.736 --> 00:46:19.613
- How could you? [grunts]
- Let's... Don't... [shrieks]

684
00:46:19.696 --> 00:46:21.990
- Stop! Stop!
- You fucking did this!

685
00:46:22.074 --> 00:46:23.909
- Hey! Get back here!
- [shrieks]
